Stanbic Bank s Wealth and Investment division has been named the best private bank in Kenya for the second year running at the global private banking awards.The event organized by the banker and professional wealth management magazines recognises excellence in wealth management.Stanbic Bank Head of Wealth and Investment Anjali Harkoo said the award reaffirms the bank s commitment to offering relevant wealth management solutions that cuts across investment management, through to succession planning and generational wealth transfer. This award is a great honor and we owe it to our clients for their continuous belief in us that drives our unwavering commitment to providing first class wealth planning and investment advice through our wealth and investment division. Harkoo said.